{"tid":1459133,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"奶共=2000年前賂秦","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:27:40.000Z","uid":235552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"76b143879a82d923ba35e729b69b226255fefabd","tid":1459133,"uid":235552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"小至個人，大至國家，越奶佢個胃口就越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n六國破滅，非兵不利，戰不善，弊在賂秦。賂秦而力虧，破滅之道也。 或曰:「六國互喪，率賂秦耶?」曰:「不賂者以賂者喪。」蓋失強援，不 能獨完，故曰「弊在賂秦」也。<br />\n<br />\n秦以攻取之外，小則獲邑，大則得城，較秦之所得與戰勝而得者，其實百倍;諸侯之所亡與戰敗而亡者，其實亦百倍。則秦之所大欲，諸侯之所大患，固不在戰矣。思厥先祖父，暴霜露，斬荊棘，以有尺寸之地。子 孫視之不甚惜，舉以予人，如棄草芥。今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得 一夕安寢;起視四境，而秦兵又至矣。然則諸侯之地有限，暴秦之欲無厭， 奉之彌繁，侵之愈急，故不戰而強弱勝負已判矣。至於顛覆，理固宜然。 古人云:「以地事秦，猶抱薪救火，薪不盡，火不滅。」此言得之。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n全文： <a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/resources/secondary-edu/lang/set_text/text_original_010.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fkla%2Fchi-edu%2Fresources%2Fsecondary-edu%2Flang%2Fset_text%2Ftext_original_010.pdf&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB25E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=5793d3f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/resources/secondary-edu/lang/set_text/text_original_010.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不賂者以賂者喪，我地可以做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4054ab86330391f51787f204a40792818b4d111","tid":1459133,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:14:16.000Z","msg":"有澳門 有西藏 有台灣 有香港 有蒙古 仲有中原國"},{"pid":"03992c51c7d78118453f1f092354964269528731","tid":1459133,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"斷糧 火燒糧蒼/奪糧倉 將香港資金派曬比全港市民"},{"pid":"9858f5ab9d19e1e4d8a60560abc4389120332c58","tid":1459133,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3cf96b26da1dcea6bb19ad29108cbd78b322196b","tid":1459133,"uid":235552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4054ab86330391f51787f204a40792818b4d111","tid":1459133,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:14:16.000Z","msg":"有澳門 有西藏 有台灣 有香港 有蒙古 仲有中原國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"以上都已經死左九成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再拉遠睇<br />\n<br />\n其他國家既角色就好似係以前啲諸侯<br />\n<br />\n希望其他文明國家要企硬"},{"pid":"6c5b3bbf039897e72ba5705e7338cf3a4d4a1b04","tid":1459133,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"可能係三國呢"},{"pid":"08e38713eeb1969536eb752db8a00eaebc9b38b2","tid":1459133,"uid":235552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c5b3bbf039897e72ba5705e7338cf3a4d4a1b04","tid":1459133,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"可能係三國呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:26:30.000Z","msg":"歷史真係不斷重演<br />\n<br />\n只係換左人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fdf7e5ed23b4062d52fb82fcc60458c1b23da9","tid":1459133,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:27:40.000Z","msg":"最首要做既事，<br />\n如果巴打有心，<br />\n請大家share呢句說話，大家一齊救香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果獨立調查委員會話你知&quot;無高官需要問責&quot;你係咪要接受呀？"}]}